<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9020F4A4355D17E65FE3BFAB4" authority="Bergroth, 1892" authorityName="Bergroth" authorityYear="1892" box="[151,506,1303,1328]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Rheumatobates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97B8248020F4A4355D17E65FE8BFAAB" bold="true" box="[151,330,1303,1328]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Rheumatobates</emphasis>
Bergroth, 1892
</taxonomicName>
(10 species)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB05E5A020F4A4355D17E2DFA5DF99C" blockId="8.[151,1436,1375,1544]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
Comments: 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9020F4A4354607E12FCA2FAEC" authority="Drake &amp; Harris, 1944" authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1944" box="[294,867,1375,1400]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Rheumatobates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carvalhoi">
<emphasis id="B97B8248020F4A4354607E12FD8AFAE3" box="[294,587,1376,1400]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Rheumatobates carvalhoi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E23AB020F4A43571C7E2DFCA2FAEC" author="Drake &amp; Harris" box="[602,867,1375,1399]" firstAuthor="Drake" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="269 - 272" refId="ref36955" refString="Drake, C. J. &amp; Harris, H. M. (1944) A new Rheumatobates from Brazil, with a note on R imitator (Uhler) (Hemipt. Gerridae). Revista de Entomologia, 15, 269 - 272." type="journal article" year="1944">Drake &amp; Harris, 1944</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was described from southeastern 
<collectingCountry id="F3181ECA020F4A4350457E2DFA86FAEC" box="[1283,1351,1375,1399]" name="Brazil" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(MG). According to 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9E23AB020F4A4354777EF6FD50FA07" author="Polhemus and Manzano" box="[305,657,1412,1436]" firstAuthor="Polhemus" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="302 - 320" refId="ref41948" refString="Polhemus, J. T. &amp; Manzano, M. R. (1992) Marine Heteroptera of the Eastern Tropical Pacific (Gelastocoridae, Gerridae, Mesoveliidae, Saldidae, Veliidae). In: Quintero, D. &amp; Aiello, A. (eds.), Insects of Panama and Mesoamerica. Selected Studies. Oxford University Press, Oxford, New York, Tokyo, pp. 302 - 320." type="book chapter" year="1992">Polhemus and Manzano (1992)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9020F4A4357DB7EF7FCE6FA07" authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1944" box="[669,807,1412,1436]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Rheumatobates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carvalhoi">
<emphasis id="B97B8248020F4A4357DB7EF7FCE6FA07" box="[669,807,1412,1436]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">R. carvalhoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the only member of the 
<emphasis id="B97B8248020F4A4351127EF7FB08FA07" box="[1108,1225,1413,1436]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">aestuarius</emphasis>
group of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9020F4A4350717EF6FF29FA5B" authorityName="Bergroth" authorityYear="1892" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Rheumatobates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97B8248020F4A4350717EF6FF29FA5B" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Rheumatobates</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to occur outside of the Eastern Tropical Pacific. Based on the ecology, taxonomy, and geographical distribution of the species of the group, those authors mentioned having serious doubts concerning the validity of the locality data of the type-series of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9020F4A43574C7E83FD52F993" authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1944" box="[522,659,1520,1544]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Rheumatobates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carvalhoi">
<emphasis id="B97B8248020F4A43574C7E83FD52F993" box="[522,659,1520,1544]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">R. carvalhoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Being so, the Brazilian record of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0F25D9020F4A4351547E83FB5AF993" authorityName="Drake &amp; Harris" authorityYear="1944" box="[1042,1179,1520,1544]" class="Insecta" family="Gerridae" genus="Rheumatobates" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carvalhoi">
<emphasis id="B97B8248020F4A4351547E83FB5AF993" box="[1042,1179,1520,1544]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">R. carvalhoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is not considered here.
</paragraph>
